nodes.text: This unidentified individual was a podracer pilot who raced using a Radon-Ulzer podracer, residing on the planet Muunilinst.
In 0 ABY, the pilot was among the five podracers who raced against the Rebel pilot Luke Skywalker, who ultimately won the race on the outskirts of Pilaan, the capital city of Muunilinst.
